                    <span>This has been a really good buy for me as a novice on flash actionscript programming. Phillip is writing in such a way that it was easy for me to understand, and follow the book.<p>It's a must have for beginners I think.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">XML example and companion website</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
